import axios from 'axios'
import {GET_GENRE, GET_ACTIVE_GENRE} from '../constan/movie'
import {GET_GENRE_API} from '../constan/api'

export const GetGenre = () => ({
    type : GET_GENRE,
    payload : axios.get('https://api.themoviedb.org/3/genre/movie/list?api_key={{API_KEY}}&language=en-US')
})
